OL,3,CCar parking rules are changing `
OL,4,Chere's what you need to know
OL,6,FBy Producer Jamel Smith
OL,8,FPrivate parking companies have been
OL,9,Faccused of introducing a "watered-
OL,10,Fdown" code of conduct on penalties for
OL,11,Fdrivers.
OL,13,FThe British Parking Association (BPA)
OL,14,Fhas hailed its new code of conduct is
OL,15,Fa "key milestone" which will "deliver
OL,16,Ffairer and more consistent parking
OL,17,Fstandards for motorists".
OL,19,FHowever, the trade association has
OL,20,Fattracted criticism as its reforms do
OL,21,Fnot include a cap on parking charges.
