OL,6,FThe new code comes into force from
OL,7,FOctober 1 this year, all newly opened
OL,8,Fcar parks must adhere to these new
OL,9,Frules. Existing car park operators
OL,10,Fhave until the end of 2026 to comply
OL,11,Fwith the regulations.
