OL,3,CCar parking rules are changing `
OL,4,Chere's what you need to know
OL,6,FPrivate parking companies have been
OL,7,Fseen as a rip off with some accusing
OL,8,Fthem of using misleading signs,
OL,9,Faggressive debt collection, and
OL,10,Fcharging unreasonable fees.
OL,12,FAnalysis of government data by the
OL,13,Fmotoring research charity, the RAC
OL,14,FFoundation, found that 9.7 million
OL,15,Ftickets were issued to drivers by
OL,16,Fprivate parking companies in Britain
OL,17,Fbetween April and December last year,
OL,18,Fequivalent to nearly 35,300 every day.
