OL,6,FA bill received Royal Assent in March
OL,7,F2019 and had been aimed to introduce a
OL,8,Flegislation-backed code of conduct.
OL,10,FIt proposed to set a limit on fines
OL,11,Ffor most parking violations, establish
OL,12,Fa more equitable appeals process and
OL,13,Fprohibit the use of aggressive
OL,14,Flanguage on tickets.
OL,16,FHowever, the government withdrew the
OL,17,Fbill in June 2022 following a legal
OL,18,Fchallenge from parking companies.
