OL,3,CCar parking rules are changing `
OL,4,Chere's what you need to know
OL,6,FThe AA criticised the new sector
OL,7,Frules, saying they lack "desperately
OL,8,Fneeded" measures like a new cap on
OL,9,Fcharges.
OL,11,FIts head of roads policy Jack Cousens
OL,12,Fsaid: "It's somewhat ironic that after
OL,13,Fpushing so hard against adopting a
OL,14,Fcode, the two bodies have decided to
OL,15,Fimplement their own.
OL,17,F"This watered-down code of practice
OL,18,Ffalls far short of the standards the
OL,19,FAA, government and consumer groups
OL,20,Fhave called for across many years.
